Question: A blue spotted sting ray sits on the ocean floor.

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a blue spotted sting ray in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a blue spotted sting ray in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the sting ray sitting on the ocean floor?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the sting ray sitting on the ocean floor?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
